          ]
        }
      },
      {
        type: 'conclusion',
        content: {
          title: "Looking Forward ðŸš€",
          sections: [
            {
              text: "This is just the beginning of my journey with AI and programming. There's so much more to explore and learn.",
              type: "reflection"
            },
            {
              text: "Key takeaways from my experience:",
              points: [
                "AI can be a powerful learning companion",
                "Start with small projects and build up",
                "Don't be afraid to experiment",
                "Share your learning journey with others",
                "Keep pushing your boundaries"
              ],
              type: "lessons"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
};
